videos.description: Kentucky's EJ Montgomery uses his whole body to block Bubba Parham's shot under the rim.
videos.headline: Montgomery stuffs shot under rim

videos.description: Kentucky registers two steals in a row and score twice, then hit two free throws to score 6 points in 7 seconds.
videos.headline: Kentucky scores 6 points in 7 seconds

videos.description: Tyler Herro steals the ball then crosses half-court to slam it.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Herro steals it then jams it on breakaway

videos.description: Tyler Creammer hits VMI's 19th 3-pointer of the game, an opponent record at Rupp Arena.
videos.headline: VMI sets 3-point record at Rupp Arena
